  "2213330": {
    "name": "3D找茬2",
    "steam_appid": 2213330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找茬新维度：探索3D微缩世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 还在盯着平面图片苦苦找不同？那可是太 2D 了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来试试全新续作《3D找茬2》吧！我们为你精心制作了一个个袖珍景观，让日常场景变得生动而灵动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和传统找茬不同，这里你可以转动、平移视角，从任何角度去观察。是的，找茬游戏也可以这么精美生动！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/98cb7c7c88823c3087e6488cad744125.poster.avif?t=1772181046\" width=622 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/98cb7c7c88823c3087e6488cad744125.webm?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/98cb7c7c88823c3087e6488cad744125.mp4?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>愿你被世界温柔以待</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你温柔地对待这个世界，我们希望你也被它温柔以待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个<strong>完全不用着急</strong>的游戏：在这里，没有倒计时，没有错误惩罚，你可以完全按照自己的节奏慢慢体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泡一杯热茶，坐在窗边，伴着轻柔音乐，雨声或阳光洒落，享受只属于你的静谧时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你遇到难找的差异时，可以使用<strong>提示功能</strong>标记出差异所在的区域，你可以放心使用，次数会定时补充。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/b9ea4be333511355fba7ed9eba6a23e0.poster.avif?t=1772181046\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/b9ea4be333511355fba7ed9eba6a23e0.webm?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/b9ea4be333511355fba7ed9eba6a23e0.mp4?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每一双眼睛都能看见的美好</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都应该有机会看见微缩世界的细腻与温暖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为此，提供了三种色盲模式：红色盲、绿色盲和蓝色盲，让你捕捉场景中的光影、色彩与微妙变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 无论视觉感知如何，微小的差异、隐藏的细节，都在静静等你发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/83a694e8ba02c5e36898bd46924dbc47.avif?t=1772181046\" alt=\"Accesibility\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这份乐趣可以分享！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个人玩是放松，两个人玩就是欢乐加倍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《3D找茬2》现在支持<strong>本地双人模式</strong>！叫上朋友或家人，拿起手柄，看看谁能更快发现不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那些“啊！我怎么没看到！”的瞬间，往往比答案本身更让人难忘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/e953e34f04e60d4371d86f885a3028da.poster.avif?t=1772181046\" width=622 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/e953e34f04e60d4371d86f885a3028da.webm?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/e953e34f04e60d4371d86f885a3028da.mp4?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的冒险，你做主</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想玩哪个场景，就玩哪个！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《3D找茬2》提供非线性关卡，没有复杂的解锁要求。你可以随时开始，随时暂停，把游戏轻松融入你的碎片时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了，游戏里还藏着独特的收藏品，全部集齐后，会不会触发意想不到的小惊喜呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/bb71f852d29d0edd0ff2ad5070da92be.poster.avif?t=1772181046\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/bb71f852d29d0edd0ff2ad5070da92be.webm?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/bb71f852d29d0edd0ff2ad5070da92be.mp4?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>定格美好：记录专属瞬间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新照片模式，让你捕捉每一个奇思妙想的发现瞬间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置边框、贴纸与创意效果，让你的作品充满个性与趣味。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分享你的创意，让朋友们也感受到你探索微缩世界的喜悦与温暖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/120e301cb960c95dbbfcfc26140ecdfe.poster.avif?t=1772181046\" aria-label=\"Photo Mode\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/120e301cb960c95dbbfcfc26140ecdfe.webm?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213330/extras/120e301cb960c95dbbfcfc26140ecdfe.mp4?t=1772181046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来《3D找茬2》，在微缩世界里找到属于你的宁静与惊喜吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 韩语, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 土耳其语, 加泰罗尼亚语, 荷兰语, 泰语, 菲律宾语, 马来语, 印度尼西亚语",
